Object.value: Pesellino, Francesco (500025682) 'child of' Francesco di Stefano (500115793);

Important Renaissance artist, noted for small panel paintings a few larger works. According to the catasto (land registry declaration) return of his grandfather Pesello, Francesco di Stefano was five years old in 1427. He was the son of the painter Stefano di Francesco (d 1427), who married Pesello's eldest daughter.
nickname, his grandfather's name was Pesello
